said. \u201cIn this regard, a discussion with Nepal Telecom has taken place. All activities related to the university will be put on the university\u2019s website,\u201d he said.\n\nLikewise, the University has issued the Examination Operation, Management and Evaluation Directive, 2077.","title":"Far-Western University to take exams online - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/07/125783/","video":[]}
